  <description><![CDATA[<p>Chalet Arnica is an attractive chalet apartment on the edge of the piste, sleeping up to fourteen people - it is ideal for a group of family and friends travelling to <span> </span><a data-udi="umb://document/4c93b881bd494483871697b278b37899" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c93b881bd494483871697b278b37899}" title="La Rosière">La Rosiere</a>.  Our chalets are on hand to help, you can enjoy six days of chalet catering including a skiers breakfast, afternoon tea and delicious evening meals with wine included. Chalet Arnica is shared with our sister company Esprit Ski who specialise in family ski holidays.<span></span></p>
<h2>Piste-side location</h2>
<p>If you like hitting the slopes as early as possible and getting back in time for the après ski, you'll benefit choosing this catered ski chalet. Located 150 metres from the ski lifts and you'll be able to get on and off the slopes with ease - perfect for the keen skiers and snowboarders looking for catered accommodation in a great location.</p>
<h2>Ideal for sole occupancy groups </h2>
<p>With attractive bedrooms and the possibility to accommodate up to 14 people, invite your family and your friends to spend a week in this cosy chalet. <span>The open-plan lounge and dining area is a mix of traditional and modern with tiled flooring, a welcoming fireplace - it</span> is a great spot to catch up with your family and friends with a bit of cake and a coffee after a day on the slopes. There is also a shared sauna for guests staying in the Ferme D'Elisa chalets.</p>
<h2>Family friendly</h2>
<p>Chalet Arnica is perfect for families, it is shared with our sister company Esprit Ski who specialise in family skiing holidays and childcare. La Rosiere is one of Esprit's main hubs for childcare, which can include infant care, Snow Club, Xtra lessons and Mountain Academy. Children booked into Esprit children’s ski lessons will be collected by our Esprit Rangers from the chalet and taken to the ski school meeting place. When booking this chalet with Inghams you can book your children into our Esprit childcare, just give our Reservations team a call to book. </p>
<h3><span>Our chalets are going greener, so our mountains don't</span></h3>
<p>Our menu is changing for the better. In all of our chalets we're giving you more choice, with both meat-free and meat options on offer throughout your stay. This is driven as part of our commitment to reduce our <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/67e40dbb55ff45098496ea2e7eee1f72" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/about-us/sustainability" target="_blank" title="Sustainability">carbon footprint</a>.</p>]]></description>
