  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Accommodation summary</strong></p>
<p><strong>Ground floor</strong></p>
<p>Shared sauna and ski and boot room for the Ferme d'Elisa Chalets is on the ground floor, as is the Esprit Snow Club room.</p>
<p><strong>First floor</strong></p>
<p><span>The comfortable accommodation occupies the whole of the first floor of the Ferme d'Elisa building and offers well-designed inter-connecting family suites and rooms, as well as one twin room, with all the bedrooms having either private or en suite bathrooms. The open-plan lounge and dining area is a mix of traditional and modern with tiled flooring, a welcoming fireplace, comfortable sofas and wood panelling.</span></p>
<p> </p>
<p><span><strong>Room description</strong></span></p>
<p><strong>Suite 1</strong> sleeps four, and has a double room and twin bunks in an interconnecting sleeping area, shower and wc</p>
<p><strong>Suite 2</strong> sleeps four, and has a double room and twin bunks in an interconnecting sleeping area, shower and wc</p>
<p><strong>Room 3</strong> sleeps two, and has twin beds, shower and hand basin and adjacent private wc, off the hallway.</p>
<p><strong>Suite 4</strong> sleeps four, this quad room has a double bed and twin beds in two sleeping areas separated by furniture and a curtain with bath/shower, wc and balcony</p>
<p>Suites 1 &amp; 2 and Room 3 will take a cot, and Sutie 4 will take up to two cots.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><img style="width: 500px; height: 353.515625px;" src="/media/13100511/chalet-arnica-floor-plan.jpg?width=500&amp;height=353.515625" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/6af446e7c08a4d6ba9176f48b9726e69" /></p>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
